Continue to enjoy all the park has to offer including;
•	Kids rides and clinics; 
•	Empowering women by offering women specific rides and clinics;
•	Adaptive trails and assistance for individuals with special needs;
•	A safe alternative for cycling away from the dangers of road riding;
•	A venue for race promoters to hold events;
•	Guided night rides;
•	A safe environment for families to gather and enjoy the breathtaking views and trails;
•	Community wellness as more and more people are coming out to ride and exercise;
•	Promoting unity in the community through volunteerism;
•	Providing a venue for students in the community to earn community service hours to meet credits for graduation.
